And the Petitioners doe likewiſe humbly returne all poſſible thanks unto this Honourable Houſe, for the great
honour and high favour vouchſafed, in giving them leave to nominate the Perſons to whom the Militia of this City ſhould be committed;
And for accepting and approving of the Nomination and return made to this Honourable Houſe, by the Petitioners on that behalfe.
